name: Alpha Life
description:
Hello! this is my latest artwork that i have mint on 19 Dec 2021. I made this when I was so low. I put all of my heart and feeling into a form of painting then I make it for 1 /1 edition to represent a super special thing. 
-
In the end, you just need some adjustments in life whenever it is not suitable to your utopia dream. You only live once, so make it such a beautiful life for ourselves. 

You may be being in pain, abandoned by people who you love, and underestimated. Enjoy it! Just keep step forward then someday you'll reach out your own Utopia! On that time you will see all the pain you have passed only be on your rear-view mirror.

-eliscosmicbae-
